=====================================
|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME        |
-------------------------------------
|0 |SUBPLAN FILTER     |            |
|1 |├─TABLE RANGE SCAN |t1(c1_index)|
|2 |└─SCALAR GROUP BY  |            |
|3 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|t2(a1_index)|
=====================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
